snippet.title: Partum Artifex - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Partum Artifex is a puzzle horror game that features creative and challenging puzzles while telling a gruesome story about a failed artist. Now he wants people to see his new kind of art, something that surely will grab everyone's attention.

STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2069760/Partum_Artifex/
